Built-ins
----------

- Add builtins for various tasks:
 set, unset, env, export,
 cd,
 for, while, if,
 etc...

Scrollback
----------

- Allow scrolling back and forth (using arrow keys)
- Add command history support

Environment
-----------

- Allow listing and modifying environment

Command interpretation/Syntax
-----------------------

- Add support for setting environment variables from cmdline
- Define shell syntax and/or language
- Bracket, quote expansion

Misc
-----

- Add support for file redirection
- Add signal handling
- Support for background/foreground tasks